# Architecture Overview â€“ HR Security Hardening Lite

## Application Scope
Scoped application built using ServiceNow Studio.

## Core Table
HR Confidential Request (u_hr_conf_request)

Fields:
- Title
- Description
- SSN Last 4 (Sensitive)
- Owner
- Requested For
- Status
- HR Notes

## Design Philosophy
Security-first architecture:
- Restrict at table level
- Refine at field level
- Protect API endpoints
- Enforce ownership visibility
